'''Braeside High School''' is a [[high school]] in [[Lavington, Nairobi|Lavington]], [[Nairobi]], [[Kenya]], operated by [[Braeburn Schools Kenya|Braeburn Schools Kenya Limited]]. It is a co-educational international day school which charges fees, is open to students of all backgrounds, and uses the [[British National Curriculum]].
